<br />

<br />
Chrononostrum line (same as above but works on shorter dur spells):
<br />
<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=3846&source=Live" target="_blank">http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=3846&source=Live</a>
<br />

<br />
